channel.title: Command Generator 1.1
channel.description:
I tried to make this as noob friendly as i could, with out all the question buildup, remember its V 1.1 My new one will be in a GUI
make a batch file with this in it [code] @echo off :co1 set b=0 set t=7 :co2 color 0f :menu cls title Command Generator 1.1 echo Welcome to the command maker, Its 90 percent noob friendly echo the only thing you need to know is were to place the codes I echo generate. Well, Lets get started! echo. echo Type "tele" to make a teleport command. echo Type "cmd" for normal command. echo. set /p c=Option: if %c%==tele goto tele if %c%==TELE goto tele if %c%==cmd goto cmd if %c%==CMD goto cmd goto er :cmd title Command Generator 1.1 cls echo Ok, Command it is then, please answer the followng questions so i can generate echo your command. echo. SET /P c=How many items will you be adding (1-8)? if %c%==1 goto 1 if %c%==2 goto 1 if %c%==3 goto 3 if %c%==4 goto 4 if %c%==5 goto 5 if %c%==6 goto 6 if %c%==7 goto 7 if %c%==8 goto 8 goto er :tele title Command Generator 1.1 cls echo Well, i see your to lazy to walk so you picked to make a teleport command. echo Please fill in the questions i ask you so i can generate your echo command. echo. SET /P N=What is the name of the command? SET /P X=What is the X coord you would like to be teled to? SET /P Y=What is the Y coord you would like to be teled to? echo. echo Generating.. Please Wait.. ECHO. >>"%N% command.java" ECHO. if (command.startsWith("%N%")) >>"%N% command.java" ECHO. {>>"%N% command.java" ECHO. teleportToX = %X%;>>"%N% command.java" ECHO. teleportToX = %Y%;>>"%N% command.java" ECHO. }>>"%N% command.java" goto er :1 title Command Generator 1.1 cls SET /P N10=Name of the command? SET /P id10=Item ID? SET /P Amount10=Amount? echo Generating.. Please Wait.. ECHO. >>"%N10% command.java" ECHO. if (command.startsWith("%N10%")) >>"%N10% command.java" ECHO. {>>"%N10% command.java" ECHO. addItem(%id10%, %Amount10%);>>"%N10% command.java" ECHO. }>>"%N10% command.java" echo Done. GOTO menu1 :2 title Command Generator 1.1 cls SET /P N19=Name of the command? SET /P id19=Item ID? SET /P Amount19=Amount? SET /P id29=Item ID? SET /P Amount29=Amount? echo Generating.. Please Wait..
